                </ul>
                <li>Income Investing:</li>
                <ul>
                    <li>Focuses on stocks that provide regular income through dividends.</li>
                    <li>Suitable for investors seeking a steady income stream.</li>
                </ul>
                <li>Day Trading:</li>
                <ul>
                    <li>Involves buying and selling stocks within a single trading day.</li>
                    <li>Focuses on short-term price movements.</li>
                </ul>
            </ol>
        </div>
        <div class = 'takeaway'>
            <h2>Takeaway</h2>
            <p>
                Investing in stocks offers a dynamic way to grow your wealth and participate in the 
                success of various companies. By understanding the different types of stocks and the
